[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ふむ……ふむふむふむ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "うん。なかなか良さそうね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "店主",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おお。これに目を留められるとは、お目が高い",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ふふ。いい品を並べているわね。\n他にも色々隠しているんでしょう？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "店主",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おや、お見通しですか。では、秘蔵の品を",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "あら。想像以上ね……ふむ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "これ、どれくらい用意できるかしら？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "店主",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ふっ。これだけの量では不足ですかな？　\n値は張りますぞ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ふふ。買えそうにもない相手には、\n存在すら悟らせないのでは？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "店主",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "仰る通り、表には出せない品ですからな。\n内密にお願いしますよ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ええ。大切な秘密を曝け出すほど、野暮じゃないわ。\nそうね、これくらい欲しいのだけど？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "店主",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "なんと！　少々特殊な伝手を使いますので、\nお時間をいただきますが、よろしいですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ええ、お願いするわね。あとは、これと――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "不穏だな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "マクダ",
		"romanized_name": "Magda",
		"model_path_hash": "9031925149745762703",
		"text": "そうか？　ただの菓子屋に見えるが？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2266739299589054477",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "ああいう店に裏の顔がある場合もある",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "今でこそ比較的大人しくしているが、\n奴は罪に問われた非合法組織、元極夜の錬金党の党首だ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "再び動き出した可能性は、大いにある。\n考えすぎかもしれないが、王国には責任があるのだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "マクダ",
		"romanized_name": "Magda",
		"model_path_hash": "9031925149745762703",
		"text": "そういうモンかね？\nまあ、油断も隙もねえ相手じゃあるけどよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2266739299589054477",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "頼むぞマクダ。私は……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "マクダ",
		"romanized_name": "Magda",
		"model_path_hash": "9031925149745762703",
		"text": "へいへい。言われなくても、お前の言いたいことは\n分かってるよ。ったく、人使いが荒い奴だぜ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2266739299589054477",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（折しもリンデ祭を目前に、人々の心が浮つく時期だ。\n　王国の治安のため、一層警戒せねば）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ・アメルハウザー",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda Amelhauser",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "優れた才を持つ、元「極夜の錬金党」党首の錬金術士。\n街を歩いて店を回り、何やら品定めをしている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ブラッドリー・カーン",
		"romanized_name": "Bradley Khan",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "通称「ブラッド」。ランターナ王国錬金爵。\n元「極夜の錬金党」党首のクリセルダを警戒している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "マクダ・キュプカー",
		"romanized_name": "Magda Kupker",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "王都では名の知れた「喧嘩屋」。\n腕が立つため、ブラッドに雇われている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2266739299589054477",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]